        "title": "WrestleMania XXVI",
        "description": "On this week's episode of ARN, Arn and Conrad discuss WWE WrestleMania XXVI from 2010 in Phoenix, Arizona! This event featured a main event rematch between The Undertaker and Shawn Michaels, with HBK's career on the line vs. The Streak! Plus, John Cena vs. Batista for the WWE Championship, Chris Jericho vs. the returning Edge for the World Heavyweight Championship, Randy Orton vs. Cody Rhodes vs. Ted DiBiase Jr., Bret Hart vs. Vince McMahon, Rey Mysterio vs. CM Punk, Triple H vs. Sheamus, a Money In The Bank Ladder match, and many more! Hear Arn's thoughts on all the matches as well as the build up and the talent involved, as well as some news from the era, including negotiations to put The Ultimate Warrior into the WWE Hall Of Fame, Tommy Dreamer leaving the company, Shane Helms, Paul Burchill and more getting their releases, his thoughts on the grind that is WrestleMania week, performing in stadiums and so much more!\n\nTurn on your notifications at www.ArnShowOnYouTube.com\nLet us help you save some money and get out of debt today over at www.SaveWithConrad.com\nIf you want the world to hear about the exciting things your doing in your business then you need to advertise on ARN! We can help make a difference in your company today over at www.AdvertiseWithConrad.com\nWe are always coming up with new hilarious t-shirt designs over at www.ArnShirts.com head over there now and check them out!",
