        "title": "Elimination Chamber 2018",
        "description": "On this week's episode of ARN, Arn and Conrad discuss WWE Elimination Chamber 2018! The card included a main event Elimination Chamber, with the winner going on to a Universal Championship match at Wrestlemania, and included Roman Reigns, John Cena, Seth Rollins, Braun Strowman, Finn Balor, Elias, and The Miz! Plus Nia Jax vs. Asuka, Matt Hardy vs. Bray Wyatt, A woman's Elimination Chamber match featuring Alexa Bliss, Sasha Banks. Mickie James, Bayley, Sonya DeVille and Mandy Rose, and more! Hear all about Arn's thoughts on the card, plus talk about the upcoming AEW PPV this weekend, and the long awaited Cody vs. MJF match, Ronda Rousey's WWE run, MMA and WWE crossover talents, Brock Lesnar as an all around performer, Jason Jordan's neck injury, the Booker T/Corey Graves situation, the return of the XFL, 205 Live and Adam Pearce, Seth Rollins and overexposure, Luke Gallows and Karl Anderson, and much more!\nYou can enjoy this episode and other clips of ARN everyday on YouTube! Subscribe and turn on your notifications at www.ArnShowOnYouTube.com\nLet us help you save some money and get out of debt today over at www.SaveWithConrad.com\nIf you want the world to hear about the exciting things your doing in your business then you need to advertise on ARN! We can help make a difference in your company today over at www.AdvertiseWithConrad.com\nWe are always coming up with new hilarious t-shirt designs over at www.ArnShirts.com head over there now and check them out!",
