        "title": "SuperBrawl II ",
        "description": "On this week's episode of ARN, Arn and Conrad discuss WCW SuperBrawl II, which included a main event of WCW Champion Lex Luger defending the title against Sting, in Lex's final WCW match for over three years, as he was headed north for his WWE run. Plus, two former WWE IC Champions collided, as Rick Rude took on Ricky Steamboat, and Arn himself laced up the boots, teamed up with Bobby Eaton, and defended the WCW Tag titles against The Steiner Bros. Also on the card, Cactus Jack vs. Ron Simmons, a legendary bout between Brian Pillman and Jushin Liger, plus Dustin Rhodes, Barry Windham, Marcus Bagwell, Steve Austin, Vinnie Vegas, Terry Taylor and more! Hear all about Arn's thoughts on the WCW landscape and product at the time, plus all the news from all over the pro wrestling world in early 1992!\n\nYou can enjoy this episode and other clips of ARN everyday on YouTube! Subscribe and turn on your notifications at www.ArnShowOnYouTube.com\nLet us help you save some money and get out of debt today over at www.SaveWithConrad.com\nIf you want the world to hear about the exciting things your doing in your business then you need to advertise on ARN! We can help make a difference in your company today over at www.AdvertiseWithConrad.com\nWe are always coming up with new hilarious t-shirt designs over at www.ArnShirts.com head over there now and check them out!",
