        "title": "Royal Rumble 2015",
        "description": "On this week's episode of ARN, Arn and Conrad discuss one of the more infamous Royal Rumbles in WWE history, Royal Rumble 2015 from Philadelphia, PA! Daniel Bryan had just returned from injury, and the WWE Universe was hopeful for a repeat performance from The Yes Movement and Bryan's fantastic Wrestlemania XXX including his title victory to close the show; however, RAW Superstar Of The Year Roman Reigns was in the midst of a huge push, and the crowd was just starting to resent it. With those two as the clear favorites, who would come out on top and head to Wrestlemania, and what was Arn's opinion on the structure of the Rumble that year, and its controversial winner?\nAlso on the card, Brock Lesnar as WWE Champion defended his title against John Cena  and Seth Rollins, The Usos vs. Miz/Sandow for the WWE Tag Team Championship, the Bellas, Paige, The Ascension, The New Age Outlaws, The New Day, Cesaro and more!\nPlus, Arn discusses the state of the locker room after CM Punk left the year before, his reaction to and conversations about Bryan's injuries, John Cena as WWE Champion in 2015, HHH & Stephanie McMahon as The Authority, \"Macho Man\" Randy Savage going into the WWE Hall Of Fame, and so much more!\nThe easiest way to support the show is to subscribe, leave a review, and tell a friend! www.ArnShow.com has the direct link to listen online or just tell a friend to search for \"ARN\" anywhere they enjoy podcasts!\nThe next best way to support the show is to buy a shirt and get a call from Arn: www.ArnShirts.com\nSave yourself some money by consolidating your debt and getting a lower mortgage payment: www.SaveWithConrad.com",
