        "title": "Clash Of The Champions X",
        "description": "On this week's Grilling JR with WWE Hall Of Famer Jim Ross & Conrad Thompson, the topic is Clash of The Champions X! Headlined by Arn Anderson joining his Horsemen brethren Ric Flair and Ole Anderson to take on The DragonMaster, Buzz Sawyer, and The Great Muta! But The Horsemen kicked out Sting earlier in the evening in one of the best segments in history; Sting would be sure to try and come collect some revenge, with unfortunate consequences. Plus, some of the biggest tag teams at the time squared off, as The Steiner Bros. wrestled Doom (Ron Simmons & Butch Reed,) and The Road Warriors took on The Skyscrapers (Dan Spivey and Mark \"The Undertaker\" Callous.) Also in action, a young Cactus Jack was booked against Mexican legend Mil Mascaras, and the story of that match and what happened after became immortalized forever in Foley's book, \"Have A Nice Day\"; what was JR's thoughts and perspective on how the match went down, and on a young Mick Foley? All this plus Kevin Sullivan, Brian Pillman, Mike Tyson vs. Buster Douglas, \"Dr. Death\" Steve Williams and so much more!\nSave yourself some money, get a better interest rate, lower monthly payments and even skip your next two payments at www.SaveWithConrad.com",
