        "title": "Royal Rumble 2005 ",
        "description": "On this week's Grilling JR with WWE Hall Of Famer Jim Ross & Conrad Thompson, the topic is WWE Royal Rumble 2005! Hear all about a card which included Triple H defending the World Heavyweight Championship against the recently dethroned Randy Orton, Shawn Michaels vs. Edge, JBL putting the WWE Championship on the line against former champions Kurt Angle and The Big Show and more! In the main event, the Royal Rumble match ended with what would've already been one of the most memorable finishes of all time, as Batista and John Cena went over the top at the same time, but thanks the an unfortunate injury sustained by a huffing, puffing, running, and diving Vince McMahon, the end of this show has become iconic for the wrong reasons, Hear all about JR's initial reaction to Vince, what he was doing coming to the ring, his injury, and what happened after he was led and helped to the back. The Rumble also included talents such as Eddie Guerrero, Chris Benoit, The Hurricane, Rey Mysterio, Booker T, Chris Jericho, and many more! All this plus news and notes from WWE and all over the wrestling world from this time period of late 2004 and early 2005!\nSave yourself some money, get a better interest rate, lower monthly payments and even skip your next two payments at www.SaveWithConrad.com",
