        "title": "TLC 2009",
        "description": "On this week's Grilling JR with WWE Hall Of Famer Jim Ross & Conrad Thompson, the topic is WWE TLC 2009! Former recent World Heavyweight Champion CM Punk opened the card against R Truth, with the Straight Edge Society and Goldust at ringside! The Undertaker continued his feud with Batista in a chairs match! A young upstart named Sheamus got his first shot at John Cena and the WWE Championship! All this plus DX vs. Chris Jericho and The Big Show, Orton-Kingston, Mickie James, Drew McIntyre, Christian, Shelton Benjamin, TNA's first Monday Night show and Bret Hart's return to WWE looming and so much more!\nWatch JR have an uncensored conversation with Jon Moxley at www.FITE.tv\nSave yourself some money, get a better interest rate, lower monthly payments and even skip your next two payments at www.SaveWithConrad.com",
