        "title": "Survivor Series '95 ",
        "description": "On this week's Grilling JR with WWE Hall Of Famer Jim Ross & Conrad Thompson, the topic is WWE\tSurvivor Series '95! The WWE was beginning to try and understand the changing times in wrestling. WCW Monday Nitro was giving fans an alternative against RAW, and ECW was giving fans an alternative to the alternative from South Philadelphia! The WWE Champion was Diesel, but history has shown he was the lowest drawing champion up to that point, and his challenger on this night was fan favorite and all time great, Bret Hart! Hear JR's thoughts on Diesel's run as champion, with Bret knocking on his door and Shawn Michaels waiting in the wings! Plus, Bill Watts' short lived WWE run around this time, Ahmed Johnson, Sycho Sid, Razor Ramon, The Undertaker, Triple H, Public Enemy in a dark match and so much more!\n\nWatch JR have an uncensored conversation with Jon Moxley at www.FITE.tv\nSave yourself some money, get a better interest rate, lower monthly payments and even skip your next two payments at www.SaveWithConrad.com",
