        "title": "A Tribute To Harley Race",
        "description": "On this week's Grilling JR with WWE Hall Of Famer Jim Ross & Conrad Thompson, the subject is \"The Greatest Wrestler On God's Green Earth,\" 8 Time NWA World Heavyweight Champion and \"The King\" himself, \"Handsome\" Harley Race!\n\nJR and Conrad go over Harley's career, from paying his dues as Happy Humphrey's driver, to his early days around the NWA territorites, his feuds with the Funks and the Briscos, traveling the world as NWA World Heavyweight Champion, championship wins and losses, passing the torch to Ric Flair, being \"The King\" in the 80s WWF, managing Lex Luger and Vader in WCW and so much more! Plus, they get a little help from Harley's friends and peers, as Hulk Hogan, Ric Flair, Eric Bischoff, Tony Schiavone, Gerald Brisco, Trevor Murdoch and more tell stories and share remberances from the legendary life and career of an absolute legend, and an all time great!\n\nRate/subscribe in Apple Podcasts! \n\nNew episodes every Thursday at 6 AM\n\nHit JR on Twitter: @JRsBBQ\n\nFind JR on Facebook/Instagram: @JimRossBBQ",
