        "title": "46: Episode 46: Starrcade 1991",
        "description": "It's Starrcade 1991, The Lethal Lottery! Find out what happens when Conrad and Tony cover what they discovered may be the worst WCW PPV of all time.  But no worries, you are still in for a hilarious time as the guys poke fun at and examine the the miscue after miscue on this very memorable episode.  There is no lack of laughs, and no lack of memorable moments!  If you don't know what the Lethal Lottery was, get ready, because it was maybe the worst and most convoluted concept for a PPV which destroyed any fan interest that might exist in the product at the time.  We know this is where Tony and Conrad shine, when they are covering a \"very WCW\" event.  Also, Arn Anderson calls Tony during the show, and Tony picks up.. ON AIR!  Feeling mischievous, they then call their friend Nature Boy Ric Flair on air!  All this, and so much more on a great episode of What Happened When Mondays!\n\n      ",
