        "title": "34: Episode 34: The \"Nature Boy\" Ric Flair",
        "description": "WOOOOO!!! The tip of the glistening iceburg that is \"Nature Boy\" Ric Flair's career, in and out of the ring, is the subject of this episode of What Happened When Mondays! Learn how Ric is responsible for Tony's career in wrestling, Ric's early world title victories, how he felt about the finish in the Starrcade 1985 match against Dusty Rhodes, and what Tony's very favorite Ric Flair match that he called was. But really, this episode is about the stories... The naked truth about Tony and Ric's partying days, the hairy trouble that Nature Boy insisted on getting into, several \"Marriott\" stories, and the truth about \"really knowing\" Ric. He is a survivor, he is the greatest of all time, and he kicked out at two and is staging the biggest comeback of his life. Ric Flair, from jet flyin' to inspiring, is the subject of this very special episode of What Happened When Mondays!\n\n      ",
